  <bioghist id="aspace_c2ce37a4a424f53a2ae82ae261254b08">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Herbert Tuttle was Professor of Modern European History at Cornell University.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_ee02d895fec16e30b74242cbcc54e0ae">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Manuscripts, lectures notes, course grade books; scrapbooks containing reviews of his published works, obituaries, letters of condolence; personal account books, and correspondence.</p>  </scopecontent>
